==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fair catch
<hw>Fair catch</hw>. <fld>(Football)</fld> <def>A catch made by a player
on side who makes a prescribed signal that he will not attempt to
advance the ball when caught. He must not then be interfered
with.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>fairground</ent>⟦br⟧
